name: Jamie Adam
description: talking about myself sometimes i really don’t know how and where to start. I am an easy going man..Shy but highly interesting person to spend spare time with.i won’t tell much about that on here. I’m described as an honest, faithful, kind,caring, passionate, and romantically fit. I might be stubborn maybe because i am independent, but deep inside me I’m just a simple and easy going man respecting my dignity. I have positive outlook and always try to see good in everything.
